{"word":"περισσός","slug":"περισσός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>περισσός, ή, όν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περί\">περί</a></el>] ‘extraordinary in number, size, or quality’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> extraordinary, in surplus, in abundance <a href='B:470 5:47'>Mt 5:47</a>; <a href='B:500 10:10'>J 10:10</a>; superfluous <a href='B:540 9:1'>2 Cor 9:1</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a> περισσοῦ</el> extremely <b><a href='B:480 6:51'>Mk 6:51</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as noun <el>τὸ περισσόν</el> <b>something more</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> expressing a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a> aspect <b><a href='B:470 5:37'>Mt 5:37</a>; advantage</b> (= extra) <b><a href='B:520 3:1'>Ro 3:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:περισσεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:περισσότερος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}